OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK government bans new     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChinese security cameras   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Government departments have been told  
OL,6, to stop installing surveillance cameras
OL,7, made by Chinese companies on "sensitive
OL,8, sites" because of security concerns.   
OL,10,FThe new policy applies to "visual      
OL,11,Fsurveillance systems" made by firms    
OL,12,Frequired by Chinese law to co-operate  
OL,13,Fwith Beijing's security services.      
OL,15,FThe government announced the move amid 
OL,16,Fconcerns among MPs about the use of    
OL,17,Fsuch equipment.                        
OL,19,FOfficials have been told to consider   
OL,20,Fremoving existing equipment entirely.  
